snippet.title: Mars Power Industries DELUXE - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW! https://store.steampowered.com/app/977230/Mars_Power_Industries_Deluxe

A relaxing puzzle game that's all about proper placement, order of operations and saturated synth vibes. Power up the colony! Find out what happened to humanity's first outer space outpost. Chill out and explore what strange devices are up there on Mars
